76561198055250612,Recommended,249650,31720479,Posted: 13 May,all,Sagil,"A great RPG based on the Dark Eye system, but with a few flaws. It's been a while since I played, but here's my take:The Good:* Engaging storyline with memorable characters* Good conversion of the Dark Eye system with a few tweaks for balance* Each combat is different thanks to hand-crafted maps with interactive environmentsThe Bad:* The Astral regeneration mechanic pretty much forces you to artificially prolong fights so that your casters can regain their astral power (as this only works during combat), making mid-to-late-game combats more painful than fun* Not available under LinuxThere also used to be a few issues with to-hit percentages not showing up correctly (showing 95% even if your chance was much less) and lack of in-game help on mechanics, but I believe these have largely been addressed now."
