he reference tags on characters/objects is distracting-No in depth character customization (but it is to be added later!)Verdict:YES pick it up, if it is on sale (erm Winter Holiday Flash sale) even better. This is a fun game to play even early access. I am glad I did it and I think the RPG community will come together to love it."
