nd them again.-The skilling system is nice but sometimes a bit annoying because I don't know when I'll find the next trainer or which skills he can teach me so I end up not really knowing where to invest my points.I'd like to state again that I think it's a great game despite a few issues and I'm having quite a lot of fun playing it."
